# PURPOSE
# -------
# Phase 1 of a before/after intervention study on discharge planning at KHCC.
# Extracts ~35 structured variables per inpatient encounter across two periods:
#   Pre-intervention : July–September 2025
#   Post-intervention: October–December 2025
#
# SOURCE TABLES
# -------------
# silver_admissions              — SPINE: one row per encounter, LOS, admission/discharge times
# GOLD_PATIENT_MOVEMENT          — ICU stay detection, surgical classification
# VISTA_PATIENTS                 — Demographics: DOB, SEX, NATIONALITY, DATE_OF_DEATH
# SILVER_DISCHARGE_SUMMARIES     — Discharge summary completion time and clinical content
# VISTA_CONSULTATIONS_REQUEST    — Consult counts, social work involvement flag
# vista_orders                   — Radiology/procedures on discharge day; meds day before
# silver_readmissions            — 7-day and 30-day readmission (pre-computed, with root cause)
# silver_er_revisits             — ED revisit within 72 hours (pre-computed)
# vista_appointment              — Post-discharge follow-up: booked before discharge, attended
#
# OUTPUT TABLE: dbo.silver_discharge_planning_structured
# OUTPUT FIELDS
# -------------
# MRN                                — Optimus-encoded patient identifier
# ADMISSION_NUMBER                   — Admission movement ID
# DISCHARGE_NUMBER                   — Discharge movement ID
# study_period                       — 'pre_intervention' or 'post_intervention'
# admission_datetime                 — Date and time of admission
# discharge_datetime                 — Date and time of discharge
# discharge_date                     — Date of discharge (date only)
# discharge_hour                     — Hour of discharge (0–23)
# los_days                           — Length of stay in days (pre-computed)
# los_hours                          — Length of stay in hours (pre-computed)
# discharged_before_noon_flag        — 1 if discharged before 12:00
# weekday_or_weekend                 — 'weekday' or 'weekend'
# admission_type                     — Raw admission type from silver_admissions
# admission_type_grouped             — Emergency/Urgent | Elective | Day Case | other
# admission_ward                     — Ward at admission
# lookup_floor / lookup_ward         — Enriched ward/floor labels
# primary_diagnosis                  — DIAGNOSIS_SHORT from silver_admissions
# attending_physician                — Attending at time of admission
# age_at_admission                   — Age in full years at admission date
# gender                             — SEX from VISTA_PATIENTS
# nationality                        — NATIONALITY from VISTA_PATIENTS
# marital_status                     — MARITAL_STATUS from VISTA_PATIENTS
# patient_type                       — PATIENT_TYPE from VISTA_PATIENTS
